OL,3,CMotorbike duo face wild fires and
OL,4,Ctough terrain as they bike to Cape Town
OL,6,FTwo Merseyside bikers are heading from
OL,7,Fthe Wirral to Cape Town.
OL,9,FDerek Charlton and Paul Gee, are seven
OL,10,Fweeks and about 7,000 miles into their
OL,11,Fmammoth 10,500 mile journey all to
OL,12,Fraise money for Children's Hospice
OL,14,FThe friends set off from Merseyside on
OL,15,F2 January 2024 and are expected to
OL,16,Farrive in the South African capital in
OL,17,FApril 2024.
OL,19,FThe first challenge for the pair was
OL,20,Fflooding in France before they reached
OL,21,FMorocco after about a week.
