OL,3,CMotorbike duo face wild fires and
OL,4,Ctough terrain as they bike to Cape Town
OL,6,FCrossing through Morocco they enjoyed
OL,7,Fsome of the last good quality roads,
OL,8,Fbut enjoyed sharing their path with
OL,9,Fsome passing camels
OL,11,FCrossing the Western Sahara gave them
OL,12,Fa real challenge, describing it as
OL,13,F"nothing but desert, sand and wind
OL,14,F....followed by more sand and more
OL,15,Fwind" the terrain became more barren
OL,16,Fand the roads more difficult to
OL,17,Fnavigate.
