OL,3,CMotorbike duo face wild fires and
OL,4,Ctough terrain as they bike to Cape Town
OL,6,F"Paul and I work great together, he
OL,7,Fguards the bikes fending off all the
OL,8,Ffixers while I deal with the
OL,9,Fauthorities."
OL,11,FThe pair have been trying to find
OL,12,Flocal places to stay, but in the vast
OL,13,Fareas they are travelling through,
OL,14,Fwild camping is often the best option.
OL,16,FIn Guinea the pair had to avoid
OL,17,Fwildfires and find a hotel to shield
OL,18,Fthem from the flames.
