OL,3,CMotorbike duo face wild fires and
OL,4,Ctough terrain as they bike to Cape Town
OL,6,FDerek said: "With both bikes loaded
OL,7,Fwith fuel bladders and water bottles
OL,8,Ffull of petrol we couldn't risk
OL,9,Fcamping, the fires were everywhere and
OL,10,Fthe acrid taste of smoke went on for
OL,11,Fmiles and miles."
OL,13,FAs well as enjoying the local wildlife
OL,14,FDerek and Paul say they have met some
OL,15,Fof the nicest and most generous people
OL,16,Fon their journey
