OL,3,CMotorbike duo face wild fires and
OL,4,Ctough terrain as they bike to Cape Town
OL,6,F"We have met some lovely people over
OL,7,Fthe last few weeks, we met some local
OL,8,Fschool children in the Ivory Coast, we
OL,9,Fcouldn't communicate with them but we
OL,10,Fgot them on our bikes and were
OL,11,Frewarded with some lovely smiles,"
OL,12,Fadded Paul.
OL,14,FThe epic adventure is all to raise
OL,15,Fmoney for Claire House, a children's
OL,16,Fhospice in Merseyside who provide end-
OL,17,Fof-life care and offer support for
OL,18,Ffamilies affected.
