OL,6,FHannah Shannon from Claire House said:
OL,7,F"We are really grateful because we can
OL,8,Fonly keep the doors of the hospice
OL,9,Fopen because of people like Paul and
OL,10,FDerek who are doing this amazing
OL,11,Fchallenge to raise money for such a
OL,12,Fgood cause.
OL,14,FYou can find more on Derek and Paul's
OL,15,Fchallenge.
